Privacy Policy for Image Compressor App

Effective Date: 23/12/24

Thank you for choosing the Image Compressor app. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your data when you use our app.

Information We Collect
Our app requires access to the following:

Gallery/Photos: To allow you to select images for compression and save compressed images back to your device.
We do not collect, store, or share any personal information or images processed within the app.

How We Use Permissions
Read Access to Gallery: This permission is used solely to allow you to select images you wish to compress.
Write Access to Storage: This permission is used to save the compressed image back to your device.
Data Storage and Sharing
We do not store, upload, or share your images or any personal information. All image processing occurs locally on your device.

Third-Party Services
Our app does not use any third-party services that collect user data.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, so we encourage you to review it periodically.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
hassanjaffery@gmail.com

By using the Image Compressor app, you agree to this Privacy Policy.
